  {
   "question": "Where does Frost Mage Phase 3 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 216 top-ranked Frost Mage DPS parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 3 (Black Temple and Mount Hyjal), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
